cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the downlink frequency band to an invalid value of 999 will cause frequency configuration errors and cell setup failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將下行頻率帶設定為無效值 999 會導致頻率配置錯誤，並造成小區設置失敗。
